Justice Bangura – Sound In Motion (EP) Canada-based Nigerian star, Justice Bangura has finally released his long awaited body of work, an extended play titled "Sound in Motion." The EP serves as a follow-up to his previous project tagged "Seasonal Lover" which was released back in November 2018. Justice Bangura is obviously not here to play this time around, the "Sound In Motion" EP houses 5 wonderful tracks, packaged and served for your listening pleasure. Much words not needed anyway. Download, listen and testify. The post Justice Bangura – Sound In Motion (EP) appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: NotJust okay